              "title": "Oil prices rise 2% to one-month high as US-Iran attacks deepen supply disruption | MarketScreener Australia",
              "type": "url_citation",
              "url": "https://au.marketscreener.com/news/oil-climbs-to-one-month-high-as-us-iran-step-up-attacks-in-strait-of-hormuz-ce7f5edcdd8ff520?utm_source=openai"
            }
